  "body": "<center>\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/title.png?raw=true\"/>\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/sWVexFEWNZ\">\n<img alt=\"Discord\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/532779726343897104?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=ffffff&labelColor=5b5a5a&color=b9855c\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mo__shark\">\n<img alt=\"X (formerly Twitter) Follow\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/twitter/follow/mo__sharky?style=for-the-badge&logoColor=ffffff&labelColor=5b5a5a&color=b9855c\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/mo_shark\">\n<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?label=&amp;color=b9855c&amp;labelColor=5b5a5a&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Patreon&amp;logoColor=ffffff&amp;url=https://shieldsio-patreon.vercel.app/api/?username=mo_shark&amp;type=patrons\"/>\n</a>\n\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/overview.png?raw=true\"/>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/bar.png?raw=true\" height=\"28\" width=\"1008\"/>\n<h2>An Origins addon that adds the Beach Crab, Deer, Moth, and Penguin origins to the game. More detailed information and mod compatibility notes can be found at our <a href=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/wiki\">Wiki</a>.</h2>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/bar.png?raw=true\" height=\"28\" width= \"1008p\"/>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/requirements.png?raw=true\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/bar_fabric.png?raw=true\" width=\"1000\" height=\"100\" />\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\">\n<img height=\"106\" width=\"316\" src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/fabric.png?raw=true\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/origins\">\n<img height=\"106\" width=\"316\" src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/origins_fabric.png?raw=true\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/pehkui\">\n<img height=\"106\" width=\"316\" src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/pekhui.png?raw=true\">\n</a>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/bar.png?raw=true\" height=\"28\" width=\"1008\"/>\n<h2 align=\"center\"><b>Click here for the Forge port! (on CurseForge)</h2></b>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/grounded-origins-forge\">\n<img height=\"106\" width=\"316\" src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/forge.png?raw=true\"/>\n</a>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/bar.png?raw=true\" height=\"28\" width=\"1008\"/>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/crab.png?raw=true\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/deer.png?raw=true\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/penguin.png?raw=true\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/moth.png?raw=true\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/bar.png?raw=true\" height=\"28\" width=\"1008\"/>\n<h3><b>This mod is sponsored by Bisect Hosting!</b></h3>\n<a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/MosMods\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/bisect_noram.png?raw=true\">\n</a>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/bar.png?raw=true\" height=\"28\" width=\"1008\"/>\n<img src=\"https://github.com/Mos-Origins/GroundedOrigins/blob/fabric/1.19/.github/assets/curseforge/credits.png?raw=true\">\n</center>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F-aarfVaHbk&amp;t\">Akto for creating a noteblock cover of the Crab Rave song</a>\n<li>EdwinMindcraft for helping in immense ways and creating the Forge port of Origins!\n<li>Apace for creating the Origins mod!\n</ul>\n",
